ruleLogicalInfo.ruleDesc: Test case to verify if any null value populated in any fields of INTRM_CLM_LINE table

paramsVOLst.paramValue:
SELECT * 
    FROM #PRM_EDW_DATABASE#.INTRM_CLM_LINE
WHERE (
 (#PRM_INCR_FLAG# = '2' AND ( UPDTD_LOAD_LOG_KEY IN #PRM_UPDTD_LOAD_LOG_KEY_EDW#  OR LOAD_LOG_KEY IN #PRM_LOAD_LOG_KEY_EDW# )) 
 
 OR
 
  (#PRM_INCR_FLAG# <> '2'AND ( UPDTD_LOAD_LOG_KEY IN #PRM_UPDTD_LOAD_LOG_KEY_EDW# OR CRCTD_LOAD_LOG_KEY IN #PRM_CRCTD_LOAD_LOG_KEY_EDW# 
  OR LOAD_LOG_KEY IN #PRM_LOAD_LOG_KEY_EDW# ))
  
  )
 AND 
   (     CLM_ADJSTMNT_KEY
    IS NULL OR CLM_LINE_NBR
    IS NULL OR CLM_LINE_SRVC_STRT_DT
    IS NULL OR BILLD_SRVC_UNIT_CNT
    IS NULL OR PAID_SRVC_UNIT_CNT
